{"tid":1447612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"響公眾地方拍攝路人係唔會犯法","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:52:27.000Z","uid":78326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c728e3a498401757049a8c798d63a252c6f010c4","tid":1447612,"uid":78326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:04:18.000Z","msg":"支持記者/網民每日直播警署外行人路擠塞情況<br />\n尋晚now直播到夜晚，一直影住尖沙咀警署門外情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直到凌晨2點幾，一路都有好多「路人」由警署行出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多時都影到佢地嘅樣貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重申我唔主張有不法之徒用呢啲片段做不法行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但作為香港市民，我好奇不同時分途經各區警署外圍市民嘅人流狀況，想做個統計，睇下現今香港人對警署嘅厭惡程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁片段作為教學使用，都需要好多參與者做分析同分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知大家有咩睇法呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n補返條link作參考之用<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jMOxmqAmV-8?t=31520\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjMOxmqAmV-8%3Ft%3D31520&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTNLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=054770c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jMOxmqAmV-8?t=31520</a>"},{"pid":"148beea80a1f5786b9ef9c56bb14cca6ab0cc659","tid":1447612,"uid":78326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:08:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2192e1cc7e8ce113f2f2ddea270cef17e8302d3d","tid":1447612,"uid":78326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:08:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e265be58e42047dae40417d4c882c4ea1ec135a9","tid":1447612,"uid":78326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:13:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2006544f500f88dec85ebfc59f2101385753c130","tid":1447612,"uid":78326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:16:07.000Z","ms